citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:29-3:01 pm on 29-
Jun-2023. The doorbell was rung multiple times, the door was knocked on multiple times, the licensee was called and
three other contacts were called, no one answered the phone and no one returned my call during the waiting period.
End Section

narrative:
2.126(b) 
   
Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries. 
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:29-3:01 pm on 29-
Jun-2023. The doorbell was rung multiple times, the door was knocked on multiple times, the licensee was called and 
three other contacts were called, no one answered the phone and no one returned my call during the waiting period. 
 
 
End Section
